{"tid":2384251,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工覺得返到身心俱疲啦","createTime":"2021-01-28T12:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T14:55:23.000Z","uid":287481,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a0acb379f3442503c38aef247749046c4f0e953","tid":2384251,"uid":287481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:28:58.000Z","msg":"係呢個部門做左兩年幾. 至從新呀姐黎左替退休呀叔一切就變天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢又幫我升左職 但升職又係變天<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日chur到死 又要呢樣又個樣 佢問你既問題要答佢心目中個answer唔岩就屌 我唔係你心入面條蟲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話就話有問題就問佢 到真係問個時又話呢個係你既問題<br />\n日日就ot 遲5分鐘返又話 都已經日日ot睇住你放工仲想點？<br />\n坐佢隔離我開始做到塞哂腦做錯做漏野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得做得越黎越辛苦 以前好鐘意講野而家全日講10句都冇<br />\n純訴苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a867b1d44e31568f9f2b51570e490372b8d911df","tid":2384251,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"工建辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa18a92d534bbc1f96e8a8b8fbb697922f24bd0","tid":2384251,"uid":287481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a867b1d44e31568f9f2b51570e490372b8d911df","tid":2384251,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"工建辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"我夠想亦開始搵工但呢段時間好難"},{"pid":"4762b512552b936c8f2321f24df05f093f77dcbf","tid":2384251,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"放工咪又變番一條好漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c02d311f543a9293b2d73fc304796a4a3590c3","tid":2384251,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa18a92d534bbc1f96e8a8b8fbb697922f24bd0","tid":2384251,"uid":287481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a867b1d44e31568f9f2b51570e490372b8d911df","tid":2384251,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"工建辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"我夠想亦開始搵工但呢段時間好難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"過完年裸辭<br />\n逼自己搵"},{"pid":"7815a110be53c51bfe21a1d7785b52393dbbcad1","tid":2384251,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"我做十幾年睇住公司同事變得好撚野蠻，工作能力同年紀正比，越老越退化，睇唔到，聽唔清楚，佢哋講嘢勁大聲，記性差咗。。。。但往往歸咎公司唔配合員工需要，電腦要用新，公司手機要夠大部，訂單唔可以有英文，訂單D字太細隻就係客人刁難佢哋，但佢哋十幾年完全冇增值過自己工作能力。"},{"pid":"a019fd297d57c244416bb0f16653344841b57207","tid":2384251,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"搵埋第日夠錢睇醫生咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}